profile_positions.description:
•	Graded weekly assignments, term-papers, and exams for classes of between 60-120 students
•	Held weekly office hours to consult with students on an individual basis about questions and issues pertaining to assignments and exams, as well as matters relating to broader course content and learning objectives;
•	Conducted weekly sections with students to expand and refine ideas and concepts presented during Professors’ lectures, work through specific examples, and provide guidance on effective ways of completing various course-related tasks (i.e. paper-writing, making a study guide, etc.)
